===Verb===
[[Category:English irregular verbs]]
{{en-verb|gives|giving|gave|given}}

#{{transitive}} To transfer the possession or holding (of something) to someone else.
#{{intransitive}} To bend slightly when a force is applied.
#{{transitive}} To estimate or predict, ''especially'' a probability.
#:I '''give''' it a 95% chance of success.
#:I '''give''' it ten minutes before he gives up.

